&lt;p&gt;Here&#039;s the room behind the kitchen.  It&#039;s in pretty bad shape.  The roof is breaking, the walls are falling apart, the door is screwed shut, the floor needs to be rebuilt, there&#039;s a hole in the back wall, the wall to the left is not even really there, and the lightbulb was dead.  Once it&#039;s completed, though, it will be a pretty awesome room, I think.  To the left is the stairs going down to the basement and the circuit box.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=../assets/images/ailihouse/house05.jpg /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;td rowspan=1 valign=center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This guy showed up at about 3:30, when the school bus came by.  His name is R.J.  He was pretty creepy, and a little too familiar with the house.  We think there was some bad business between him and the previous owner.  He helped out with some stuff, but he mostly just stood around and said random things.  I believe in this picture he was counting something in the downstairs bathroom.  Or maybe he was playing checkers on the wall.  That&#039;s enough of him.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=../assets/images/ailihouse/house26.jpg /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;td rowspan=1 valign=center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the exterior of the house.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img name=&quot;spin&quot; src=&quot;../assets/images/ailihouse/3.jpg&quot; onClick=&quot;spin()&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;td rowspan=1 valign=center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The yard is getting to pretty jungle-level proportions.  R.J. offered to mow the lawn for a couple bucks a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=../assets/images/ailihouse/house27.jpg /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;td rowspan=1 valign=center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When we got back home, Lucy was pretty tired.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=../assets/images/ailihouse/house29.jpg /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Well, that&#039;s all of the pictures I got.  If you were wanting more, you&#039;re just getting greedy.  Stay tuned for tomorrow, for the scoop on election day:  &lt;i&gt;Pointless &#039;06&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

