&lt;p&gt;I&#039;m in a digital video class this semester (now that I&#039;m a CGT major again).  Our first project was assigned on the first day of class (awesome).  The project was to create a few 30 second commercials for a company that makes video games for cell phones.  The company is called Morvid Games, and my group was called CGT 346 TeamOne.  We called ourselves that because professor Morales always called on us first to present our work.  He did that to intimidate the rest of the groups, because we regularly blew them away.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is is, commercial number one for my CGT 346 class.  It&#039;s the shortest and, in my opinion, &lt;i&gt;lamest&lt;/i&gt; of all three commercials.  Let me know how you like it, and stay tuned for number two and three.  Double click the file to see it in full screen.&lt;/p&gt;

