&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.denyconformity.com/content/olds.php?post=00164&quot;&gt;The first article, which started this whole fiasco.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.denyconformity.com/content/olds.php?post=00173&quot;&gt;The first update, with a not-so successful replacement.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

