&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;or, People are Morons&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Facebook has a new layout. I figured I would mention that in case you&#039;re my parents or you live under a rock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Of course, by &quot;new layout&quot; I mean that they slightly re-designed the home page, which is just a center for pertinent information. Who befriended whom, who says what about which, and et cetera. They redesign it once or twice a year. Every single time they do, the new layout is met with such a barrage of negative criticism, you&#039;d think a Republican was just elected president again. Of course, by &quot;negative criticism&quot; I mean mostly cursing in all caps.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Somebody decided to start a vote this time around to see who liked the new layout. As of now, the application has 80,505 votes for the new layout and 1,234,926 votes against. (or as I like to say it, 80,505 intelligent people and 1,234,926 morons). People are still voting because they think it will make a difference. Facebook neither made the application nor do they care what the outcome of the vote is.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The other thing that people are still doing is commenting on the voting application&#039;s message board. Here are some highlights of those comments, along with my reasons why they&#039;re morons.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.denyconformity.com/assets/images/fb/1.jpg&quot; /&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;So the second, third, or fourth layouts are fine? I think the first layout wasn&#039;t great, either, but who can remember &lt;em&gt;six years ago&lt;/em&gt;? Also, who doesn&#039;t like black text on a white background? You probably shouldn&#039;t read any books. You&#039;re right, though, &lt;a href=&quot;http://profile.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=user.viewProfile&amp;friendID=262334249&quot;&gt;Myspace&lt;/a&gt; is totally better.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.denyconformity.com/assets/images/fb/2.jpg&quot; /&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;What a valid argument. Or maybe this is just an act of self-censorship.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.denyconformity.com/assets/images/fb/3.jpg&quot; /&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;I&#039;m not sure you get the message behind that book you&#039;re quoting there, Paul.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.denyconformity.com/assets/images/fb/4.jpg&quot; /&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Oh, old people. Your desperate attempts to stay with the times are so futile.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

