&lt;p&gt;That&#039;s the new website for Smac, a guy who makes electronic music in his spare time. He&#039;s the one who made that &quot;Economy&quot; track I talked about a while ago. You can get that track (which is part of an eight track LP), his first single, &quot;I can do House Music&quot; or his new album, called &quot;Love Hate.&quot; They&#039;re all free, so really there&#039;s no reason not to check it out. If you like any of his stuff, feel free to let him know at SMAC [at] DENYCONFORMITY [dot] COM. Seriously, he would really appreciate your approval, and it&#039;s not like it&#039;s me or anything . . .&lt;/p&gt;

