&lt;p&gt;Happy eleven day, everybody.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

data.text:
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday02.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Fred opens his slightly less fake gift (band-aids).&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday01.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;&quot;Is it some sort of female product?&quot;&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday03.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Finally Fred gets an actual present.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday04.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Fred liked the RC car that I got him.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday05.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;He liked Chris&#039;s present, too!&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday06.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;The car in action.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday07.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Then everyone started kicking baloons at me.  (picture courtesy Cameron Marston)&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_Fredbirthday08.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Here&#039;s the previous shot, but from my perspective.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_lincolns.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;320&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I&#039;m giving the credit for this masterpiece to my sister. This picture was originally located on the official website for the Association of Lincoln Presenters. This Association is a huge club of guys who tour the country presenting as Abraham Lincoln himself. It&#039;s a really cool group, and they can explain it better than I can. Their website is &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lincolnpresenters.com&quot;&gt;www.lincolnpresenters.com&lt;/a&gt; so feel free to check them out for yourself.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
What makes this picture so great is that they somehow managed to include Abraham Lincoln, clones, the Blues Brothers, Santa Claus, the flag, and Nazis (check out Santa&#039;s salute) into one glorious picture. This picture has some strange creepyness to it, too. Santa has so many levels of scaryness here that I don&#039;t know where to begin.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_fortouiatenon.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;It&#039;s that time of year again, so I went to the Fort with my parents and we checked out the Feast of the Hunter&#039;s Moon (check my really early posts for last year&#039;s Feast). This is the &quot;fort.&quot;  Cute, huh?&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_notmanypeople.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;There weren&#039;t many people there this year, it seemed.  Maybe it was the constant threat of rain, or just a lack of interest.  It was much thinner than last year.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_outofplace.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;If you can&#039;t find some sort of humor in this image, you&#039;re either blind or just dumb.  This is an example of the quirky things you see at the Feast.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_painful.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Sounds painful, and very very difficult.  Just to pee soup would be hard, not to mention peeing soup AND coffee . . .&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_plentyfurs.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Some people make their living going from festival to festival selling various . . . items.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snakes.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Like these things.  They were honestly at almost every single booth, and everyone had them for a different price, too.  You could spend the entire day finding every price for either these wooden snakes, or wooden swords and guns.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_jugglers.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;In addition to the merchants and traders, travelling performers like the Amazing Budabi Brothers Juggling show.  These guys were really cool.  They had a very funny act that they did, and they juggled very well.  I captured a short video of their amazing juggling talents.  &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/images/weekly_image/jugglers.avi&quot;&gt;Click here to see it&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_footballtree.JPG&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I was leaving for play practice one evening, and these guys were outside throwing this football around.  One guy had the idea to punt it to his buddies.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_footballtree2.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Let&#039;s take a closer look at this tree that seems to have them all so interested.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_footballtree3.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;One of them just kept saying, &quot;I can&#039;t believe that happened!&quot;  It was so delicately balanced on that branch.  I couldn&#039;t resist, I had to take a picture of it.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20001.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I was snowing on Wednesday.  The first snow of the season, much earlier than last year.  Unfortunately my camera didn&#039;t do a very good job of capturing the snowflakes falling from the sky.  Trust me, it&#039;s snowing in this picture.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20005.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I made it to Beering and noticed a little patch of white in the grass.  I got a closer look to make sure it wasn&#039;t just chewed up styrofoam.  My frozen toungue proved that it was, in fact, snow.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20007.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;If you could see the snow falling in the background, this picture would be amazing.  I had to take a picture of the lone flower defiantly shaking its fist at the weather.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20019.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;While I was trying not to be hit by this car, I got a nice shot of the rear hood and the snow collected upon it.  The clock tower should be in every picture I take on campus, because it is the largest phallic symbol I know of.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20023.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Snow makes Cameron a happy Canadian.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20025.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I couldn&#039;t help but notice that Cameron needs to purchase a new brand of shampoo.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20029.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Again, if you could see the snow in this shot, it would be a lot better.  I was just amazed by how much green is still on the trees during the first snow of the year.  It was about this time that people were really looking at me funny.  It might have been that I was sprinting around, diving into the ground, and wearing a bowler hat.  Or maybe people are just crazy.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20035.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;More styrofoam.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_snow%20038.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;It wasn&#039;t the sunniest day in a while, and it was sure cold, but It was still a nice day to get a couple pictures and run into several friends on campus.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN45.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Some day I will recreate this shot in 3d Studio, and it will look awesome.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20016.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;PAO hall is a far better place than CA3.  Just take my word for it.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20017.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Most of these pictures don&#039;t really need captions.  I was just out today getting pictures, since it was such a nice sunny day.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20025.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I find photography somewhat cathartic.  Maybe it&#039;s because I take pictures of quiet, serene things.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20047.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;People seem to find it strange that I look around when I walk on campus.  Most people just keep their eyes glued to the sidewalk advertisements.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20020.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Clock tower.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20048.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Most people don&#039;t notice interesting things like this.  I don&#039;t notice the signs for the anime club callout.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20050.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Who is worse off?&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20052.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Frankly, I&#039;d rather be them.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20053.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Because when you always look at the ground,&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_SUN%20045.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;The sun doesn&#039;t get in your eyes.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_creepycat.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;We&#039;ll start with this one.  This is the original creepy cat picture that I got almost a year ago.  Since then, I&#039;ve been collecting any crazy cat pictures that I could find.  That&#039;s pretty weird, isn&#039;t it?&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_cat_067.jpg&quot; height=&quot;371&quot; width=&quot;347&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Imagine waking up to that thing some morning.  Terrifying.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_wet.jpg&quot; height=&quot;286&quot; width=&quot;292&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;ME HATE BATH&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_evil%20cat.jpg&quot; height=&quot;456&quot; width=&quot;566&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;This one has such a great expression.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_2658.jpg&quot; height=&quot;248&quot; width=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;This one might be Photoshopped, but it&#039;s still bizzarre.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_9032.jpg&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; width=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I&#039;ll finish off tonight with this one.  It really looks pathetic, doesn&#039;t it?  So pathetic I just want to laugh really hard at it.
&lt;br&gt;
Feel free to leave comments making up stories about any of the pictures, or voting on which one you like best.  There are plenty more where these came from.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_chip1.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Viewers, say hello to Chipotle.  &quot;Hello, Chipotle.&quot;  That&#039;s right, Chipotle is a newcomer on campus, so everyone be extra nice until Chipotle can get into the swing of things.  I know, I know, Chipotle&#039;s been going around offering everyone a free burrito.  It&#039;s supposedly Chipotle&#039;s specialty, I know, but let&#039;s just humor Chipotle and be nice, just this once.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_chip2.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;I know it&#039;s raining, but we just have do take a hit for Chipotle.  Chipotle&#039;s been working all summer for these free burritos, I guess, so get your umbrella and go out to State Street and tell Chipotle how great the free burrito is.  We just don&#039;t want to hurt Chipotle&#039;s feelings this early in the semester.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_chip3.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Oh, I guess there&#039;s a line.  That&#039;s great, show Chipotle how much we need a new burrito place in West Lafayette.  It&#039;s almost as much as we need a new pizza place.  Well, go ahead and get in line.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_chip4.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image_caption&quot;&gt;Keep your arms and legs away from traffic.&lt;/div&gt;
			
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/weekly_image/small_chip5.jpg&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; width=&quot;640&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
