&lt;p&gt;&quot;It&#039;s easy,&quot; was the reply.  &quot;Every time a doctor loses a patient here, out law says that he must fly a baloon over his office.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The tourist started searching for doctors.  One doctor had twenty baloons above his office, and another had thirty. Finally, the tourist found a doctor with only six baloons tied to his office.  He went in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&quot;You&#039;ll have to wait,&quot; the doctor said.  &quot;For someone who just started practice yesterday, I&#039;ve been very busy.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

