&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8711%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8724%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8766%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8785%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8800%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8813%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8819%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1050&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/shapes/IMG_8827%20copy.jpg&quot; height=&quot;1049&quot; width=&quot;700&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I recently became unemployed, again. Now that I&#039;m back on the job market, I figured it was time for me to put out my shingle, as it were, and offer my services as a freelance web designer. To be honest, I&#039;m a bit sick of the usual sorts of clients one has to deal with when traveling the world of freelance, so I came up with a great idea. I just recently made a post on Craigslist as a fulfillment of that idea. Check it out!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;width: 90%; margin: auto&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wanted: Genius or near-genius who needs a website&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am a Web Designer working in the Chicago area, and I would quite enjoy the opportunity to build a website for you, provided you are very intelligent and are capable of forming complete sentences. I have worked for many years with clients on projects ranging from completely dumb to merely boring, and I can apply my years of experience to your project - just give me a project that isn&#039;t a complete insult to that experience.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Perhaps your Mensa chapter need a new website, or your company that trains college professors needs a database to keep track of your textbooks. Perhaps you need a content management system for your rocket science projects, or you finally want to advertise your skills of brain surgery. If you are really serious about your job, and you acknowledge that I am too (and therefore do not need you to tell me how to do it), your new website is only a few weeks (and a reasonable amount of money) away!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I do not claim to be a genius, I only wish to work with them. I will not purport to be smarter than you, provided you respect me enough to do the same. This is a real and honest solicitation of my services. Examples of my work are, of course, available upon request.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please contact me with a summary of your web project, the institution where you have acquired your PhD, your most recent IQ test scores, and the answers to the following questions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do you know what the Internet is?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do you respect professionals and give them the freedom to do their jobs?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On a scale of one to ten, how much could you possibly care less about the difference between Helvetica and Arial typefaces?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How often do you &quot;change your mind&quot; about important decisions related to things like design or style?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How badly do you want to avoid attracting website visitors that use Internet Explorer?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Which is more important to you: White Space or Outer Space?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No small business owners, evangelists, print designers, or otherwise unnecessary persons need apply.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Shauvon McGill&lt;br&gt;
Professional Internetman&lt;br&gt;
http://www.denyconformity.com&lt;/p&gt;

