&lt;p&gt;Every picture submitted to PIN15 will be analyzed and saved in one of the two dude picture categories. Is it a picture of a boob? Is it a picture of a butt? Is it a useless picture of something else? You don&amp;rsquo;t have to wonder any more! Now dudes will be able to go to the PIN15 website and browse through all of the pictures submitted by other dudes and go right to the exact type of picture you want. The best part is that you never have to worry about having to look at a picture that isn&amp;rsquo;t of a butt or a boob.&lt;/p&gt;

