&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;a href=&quot;/assets/images/brickworld/2015/brickworld2015-15.jpg&quot; target=&quot;denyconformity&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/brickworld/2015/small/small-brickworld2015-15.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;That little orange ball thing at the top of this wizard tower was spinning, I believe.&lt;/div&gt;

